    "title": "Senior Teacher - LinkedIn Learning India - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "LinkedIn Learning India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Teacher for our Vadodara operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout LinkedIn Learning India:\nLinkedIn Learning India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Zoom/Teams\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with LinkedIn Learning India!",
